# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok france 's raphael poiree on thursday won the ##km individual race in the world cup biathlon - his first of the season .
# ::alignments
(w / win-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Raphael"
                  :op2 "Piree")
            :poss (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "France")))
      :ARG1 (r / race-02
            :ARG3 (d / distance-quantity
                  :quant 250
                  :unit (k / kilometer))
            :mod (ii / individual)
            :mod (b / biathlon
                  :mod (g / game
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "World"
                              :op2 "Cup")))
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1
                  :range (s / season)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok winter is the peak danger season for poisonous carbon monoxide fumes from vehicles , heaters and other appliances , federal health officials warn .
# ::alignments
(w / warn-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Federal"
                              :op2 "Health"))
                  :ARG2 (o / official)))
      :ARG1 (s / season
            :time-of (e / endanger-01
                  :ARG0 (f / fume
                        :source (a / and
                              :op1 (v / vehicle)
                              :op2 (h2 / heater)
                              :op3 (a2 / appliance
                                    :mod (o2 / other)))
                        :mod (s2 / small-molecule
                              :name n
                              :op1 "carbon"
                              :op2 "monoxide"))
                  :ARG0-of (p2 / poison-01)))
      :ARG1-of (p3 / peak-01)
      :domain (d / date-entity
            :season (w2 / winter)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok dozens of youths went on a rampage , burning vehicles and vandalising buildings in a tough paris suburb friday in an act of rage following the death by electrocution of two teenagers trying to flee police .

      :ARG0 (y / youth

                  :op1 12))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (r / rampage-01
                  :ARG0 y)
            :op2 (b / burn-01
                  :ARG0 y
                  :ARG1 (v / vehicle))
            :op3 (v2 / vandalize-01
                  :ARG0 y
                  :ARG1 (b2 / building))
            :location (s / suburb
                  :ARG1-of (t / tough-03)
                  :mod (p / paris))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (f / friday)))
      :manner (r2 / rage-02
            :ARG0 y)
      :ARG1-of (f2 / follow-01
            :ARG2 (d2 / die-01
                  :ARG1 (e / electrocute-01
                        :ARG1 (t2 / teenager
                              :quant 2
                              :ARG0-of (t3 / try-01
                                    :ARG1 (f3 / flee-05
                                          :ARG0 t2
                                          :ARG1 (p2 / police))))))))

                        :ARG1-of (c / carry-on-02)

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :poss c2)

                        :quant 1000000000
                        :unit (y / yuan)
                        :mod (t2 / total)
                        :time (h / half
                              :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                                    :value 1)
                              :part-of (y2 / year
                                    :mod (t3 / this))))
                  :op2 (r / rise-01
                        :ARG1 m2
                        :ARG2 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 1000000000
                              :unit (y3 / yuan))
                        :time (y4 / year
                              :ARG1-of (s2 / same-01
                                    :ARG2 (y5 / year
                                          :mod (l / last))))))))

                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Congo")))

                  :weekday (t / tuesday)))
      :op2 (u / urge-01
            :ARG0 o
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (g / government-organization
                        :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01))
                  :op2 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (o2 / oppose-01)))
            :ARG2 (a3 / and
                  :op1 (r2 / remain-01
                        :ARG1 a2
                        :ARG3 (c2 / commit-01
                              :ARG1 a2
                              :ARG2 (p2 / process-02
                                    :ARG1 (p3 / politics))))
                  :op2 (r3 / resolve-01
                        :ARG0 a2

                              :ARG0 a2)
                        :manner (d4 / dialogue-01)))))

                        :name (n3 / name

            :ARG0 c

                  :polarity -

      :op1 (r / register-02
            :ARG0 (e / economy)

                        :ARG2-of (h / have-degree-91
                              :ARG1 g
                              :ARG3 (m / most)
                              :ARG5 (m2 / more-than
                                    :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                                          :quant 5
                                          :unit (y / year))))))
            :time (b / before
                  :op1 (n / now)
                  :duration (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 3
                        :unit (m3 / month))))
      :op2 (b2 / believe-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (a2 / analyze-01)
                  :quant (f / few))
            :ARG1 (p2 / possible-01
                  :ARG1 (o / or
                        :op1 (s / stop-01
                              :ARG0 e
                              :ARG1 (g2 / grow-01
                                    :ARG1 e))
                        :op2 (s2 / slip-01
                              :ARG1 e
                              :ARG4 (r2 / reverse-01
                                    :ARG1 e)
                              :time (q / quarter
                                    :mod (c / current))
                              :degree (s3 / slight))))))

# ::id 1851 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok slovenia and algeria will already be playing for world cup survival when they meet in their opening group c match on sunday .
# ::alignments
(p / play-01
      :ARG0 (a / and
            :op1 (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Slovenia"))
            :op2 (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Algeria")))
      :ARG2 (s / survive-01
            :ARG0 a
            :ARG1 (g / game
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "World"
                        :op2 "Cup")))
      :time (a2 / already)
      :time (m / meet-03
            :ARG0 a
            :ARG1 (g2 / group
                  :ARG0-of (o / open-02))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / sunday))))

# ::id 1852 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok jason lezak did n't take any chances with this morning swim , qualifying first in preliminaries for the ###-meter freestyle wednesday .
# ::alignments
(c / chance-02
      :polarity -
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Jason"
                  :op2 "Lezak"))
      :ARG1 (s / swim-01
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :dayperiod (m / morning)
                  :mod (t / today)))
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (q / qualify-01
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 q
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (f / freestyle
                        :mod (d2 / distance-quantity
                              :quant 2
                              :unit (m2 / meter)))
                  :subevent-of (w / wednesday))
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)
            :subevent-of (p2 / preliminaries)))

# ::id 1853 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (p / person

                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "U.S."))
                  :ARG2 (a / ambassador
                        :location (h2 / here))))
      :ARG1 (p2 / person
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "America"))
            :ARG0-of (w / wear-01
                  :ARG1 (w2 / war)))
      :ARG2 (d / dig-in-02
            :ARG0 p2
            :purpose (h3 / haul
                  :ARG1-of (l / long-03)
                  :ARG1-of (m / mean-01
                        :ARG2 (e / effort-01
                              :ARG1 (t / transform-01
                                    :ARG1 (a2 / and
                                          :op1 (c3 / country
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Iraq"))
                                          :op2 (r / region
                                                :ARG1-of (s / surround-01
                                                      :ARG2 c3)
                                                :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                                                      :ARG2 (s2 / spot
                                                            :ARG1-of (t2 / trouble-05)
                                                            :ARG1-of (m2 / major-02)
                                                            :location (w3 / world)
                                                            :time (n4 / now))))))))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (m3 / monday)))

# ::id 1854 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok seven peacekeepers were killed and ## were wounded , seven critically , in a militia ambush on their convoy in darfur , the largest hit on a struggling , joint u.n.-african union force that took charge in january , officials said wednesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (o / official)))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (k / kill-01
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :quant 7
                        :ARG0-of (k2 / keep-01
                              :ARG1 (p3 / peace))))
            :op2 (w / wound-01
                  :ARG1 p2
                  :op3-of a)
            :ARG1 (p4 / person
                  :quant 7
                  :ARG0-of k2
                  :ARG1 p3))
      :ARG1-of (c / critical-03)
      :time (a2 / ambush-01
            :ARG0 (m / militia)
            :ARG1 (c2 / convoy
                  :poss p2)
            :location (c3 / city
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Darfur")))
      :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
            :ARG2 (l / large)
            :ARG3 (m2 / most))
      :ARG1-of (h3 / hit-01
            :ARG2 (f / force
                  :ARG0-of (s2 / struggle-02)
                  :mod (u / union-02)
                  :mod (j / joint)
                  :ARG0-of (c4 / charge-06
                        :time (d / date-entity
                              :month 1))))
      :time (w2 / wednesday))

# ::id 1855 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (a / agency
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "IRNA")

            :mod (o / official)
            :poss (c / country
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Iran")))
      :ARG1 (a2 / attribute-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Parliament")
                              :poss c)
                        :ARG2 (s / speaker)))
            :ARG1 (a3 / attack-01
                  :ARG0 (t / terrorist)
                  :ARG1 c
                  :location (s2 / southeast
                        :part-of c)
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (s3 / sunday)))
            :ARG2 (e / effort-01
                  :ARG0 (c2 / country
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "America"))
                  :ARG1 (a4 / against
                        :op1 c)
                  :mod (h2 / hostile))))

                        :op1 "Myanmar")))

            :ARG0 e

                        :mod (r2 / religious-group

                                    :op1 "Islam"))

                                    :location (c4 / country
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Asia"))))
                        :ARG1-of (e2 / embattle-01)))
            :time (v / visit-01
                  :ARG0 e
                  :time (m / month
                        :mod (n4 / next)))))

# ::id 1857 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG1 (p / pass-01
            :ARG0 (s / state
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "California"))

            :purpose (p2 / protect-01
                  :ARG0 l
                  :ARG1 (v / victim
                        :ARG1-of (v2 / victimize-01
                              :ARG0 (v3 / violence
                                    :mod (d / domestic)))))
            :duration (m / multiple
                  :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (y / year))))
      :ARG2 (h / help-01
            :polarity -
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (p3 / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Tony"
                        :op2 "Alicea"))))
